VERSION 1
WHEN PRESENT \b(strcpy|strcat|sprintf|gets|memcpy)\s*\(
WHEN EXPR MISSING:QByteArray|QString::fromUtf8|bounds|size|length && MISSING:test|example
REPORT AS area_of_interest
REASON Detects unsafe memory/string APIs in C++ code.
TRACE Externalized rule logic for Qt Unsafe Memory/String API.
